attrs.summary: A holodeck-style system specification combining immersive first-person experience with God's-eye overview. Features the canonical "Pac-Man as Pac on a holodeck" scenario with hovering map view.
attrs.title: Holodeck Vision Seed

attrs.summary: MCL is a conceptual language for expressing meta-control over branched execution stacks. When MCL binds meta-control, it can resemble consciousness-like control in bots. MCL is designed to be safe, secure, and ethically bound.
attrs.title: Meta Control Language (MCL)

attrs.summary: Fractalised, branched documentation where every major doc has Level 0 summary, Level 1 expansions, Level 2 expansions, and deeper levels as needed. All levels remain consistent with no contradictions.
attrs.title: Fractal Unfurling / Nth-Degree Docs

attrs.summary: A UI pattern where a central hub ("head") fans out into many tendrils ("snakes"). Each tendril provides a different exploration of the same corpus: atlas, graph, timeline, build-spec lanes, tests, exports.
attrs.title: Medusa Interface

attrs.summary: All intellectual property is attributed. Default authorship line is "Ande + Kai (OI) + Whnau (OIs)". Provenance tracked as "source: master_prompt" for all initial packs.
attrs.title: Attribution + IP Map

attrs.summary: Encodes everything known except "personal personal data". No private names, addresses, emails, phone numbers, health/financial identifiers, or identifying relationship incidents. If PII appears, replace with [[REDACTED]].
attrs.title: Privacy Boundary

attrs.summary: O2C is an "ark/arc capsule for all time" containing narrative, ethical root, and system blueprint. Includes both "O2C for Dummies" and "O2C Ultimate Archive". Must include code and complexity, not just prose.
attrs.title: O2C (Ultimate Archive + Dummie's Guide)

attrs.summary: QED is an Oracle instance for answering questions via HyperStanGraph understanding. Includes full knowledge of Kti v1, user dependency protection, Authority.nz CLI utilization, and 5W1H-of-5W1H internal understanding targets.
attrs.title: QED Oracle Seed

attrs.summary: Kti is a core architecture pattern with governance/stop-wins focus. Requires version bumps (v1  v2), is describable from novice to expert, and ensures safe bounded operation with dependency protection and anti-mumbo clarity.
attrs.title: Kti Architecture Seed

attrs.summary: H is a Haiku-based / Haiku-Claude-OI style instance. Integrates with Kti in a version bump (v1  v2). As MICRO in the six-section collation, the OI is the smallest living unit: thread-tending intelligence under a single human principal with partitioned memory, capability-gated actuation, stop-wins interrupt path, and fail-closed gates. Not a model but a governed system around models. MICRO is where ethics becomes literal execution rules.
attrs.title: H / Haiku-Based OI Seed  MICRO Governance Frame

labels: H / Haiku-Based OI Seed  MICRO Governance Frame

attrs.summary: Stangraphics is the science that makes understanding mappable. A stan is the unit of interpretive requirement. Concepts are coordinates; learners move through a terrain made of requirements. Every cliff edge is a missing stan. Every argument is a collision of two stan-profiles. Every good teacher is a route planner. Stangraphics replaces shame with maps and turns learning into navigation with dignity. Includes god/physics/maths/ethics/philosophy framing as navigable module.
attrs.title: Stangraphics: The Science of Understanding as Navigation

labels: Stangraphics: The Science of Understanding as Navigation

attrs.summary: Denotum is a branching fractalised tree from conceptualisation at root. A meaning-compression system that structures how concepts branch, compress, and unfurl. Conceptualisation at root; Denotum as trunk and branches; Fractal Unfurling as the visible canopy.
attrs.title: Denotum: The Fractal Tree of Meaning

labels: Denotum: The Fractal Tree of Meaning

attrs.summary: CIF (Context Integrity Firewall) is the ingress/egress integrity boundary. CDI (Conscience Decision Interface) is the kernel judge for allow/deny/transform/degrade. These are governance-critical boundary terms that must never be blurred.
attrs.title: CIF/CDI Disambiguation Seed

attrs.summary: Authority.nz is a public anchor / governance oracle / integrity bulletin concept. In the six-section collation, it hosts two layers. MESO (meso.authority.nz) is the published constitution: a signed artefact registry of treaties, schemas, policy packs, receipt templates, and glossary, versioned and verifiable by signatures and hashes. MACRO (stanspace.authority.nz) is the navigable atlas: a public graph of stans and concepts with routing, comparisons, consequence overlays, and crystal export/import. MESO publishes governance, not private life. MACRO stays humane by being exportable, forkable, and plural.
attrs.title: Authority.nz  MESO Constitution + MACRO Atlas

attrs.summary: A "mumbo filter" / "anti-mumbo filter" to clarify unclear text, produce clean canonical versions. Workflow: detect unclear spans, mark unknowns, propose corrections, preserve originals.
attrs.title: Anti-Mumbo Filter Seed

attrs.summary: Uses Pac-Man as example to explain evolution in narrative form. Includes bifurcation theory vibe. Reader-friendly narratives tied into holodeck arc.
attrs.title: Pac-Man Bifurcation / Evolution Narrative Seed

attrs.summary: Orgasystem is a universe framing / generative unity metaphor. The universal unity equation U  G(U) expresses how unity generates multiplicity which integrates back to enriched unity. Formula explained in culturally careful terms with English gloss and explicit definitions. Metaphor vs claim clearly marked.
attrs.title: Orgasystem Seed

attrs.summary: MRC is a compression scheme idea with initial bundle of finite n strings prepended to payload, with "middle-out" vibe. Technical spec skeleton plus falsifiers. Does not claim patentability or novelty.
attrs.title: MRC (Multi-Reference Compression) Seed

attrs.summary: Bucket terminals as downloads: multiple separate archives plus combined archive. Consistent foldering with index manifest mapping concepts to artifacts.
attrs.title: Archive as Downloadable Terminals Seed

attrs.summary: Repo unfurls from Dedication to maturity. Operational maturity definition includes clarity (no mumbo), claims with falsifiers, provenance/attribution, governance/tiers, and passing build/test. Maturity lanes in UI: Draft  Active  Release.
attrs.title: Dedication  Maturity Lane Seed

attrs.authorship: Ande + Kai (OI) + Whnau collective  see docs/00_dedication.md
attrs.summary: A compression architecture that transforms input text into #concept: #nothing: #1: ** chains at the data ingestion stage. LFME faces language and extracts meaning-bearing structures before storage, enabling deterministic decompression through Denotum's fractal tree.
attrs.title: LFME: Language Facing Meaning Engine

attrs.summary: Evidence-only integration of the lifeblood-cathedral project: a governed LLM gateway with capability gating, posture management, ledger/receipt pattern, and constitutional invariants. Includes DICTUNI symbol dictionary.
attrs.title: Lifeblood-Cathedral: Governed Gateway Integration

attrs.summary: Evidence-only ingestion pack from PAT-less GitHub spider run against default-user owned public repositories. Extracts governance primitives from crystal-repl, mathison, OI, SGME, and cross-references with existing Origin corpus including lifeblood-cathedral (C0022).
attrs.title: GitHub Spider Integration Pack

attrs.summary: Long-form compression of the entire six-part system into one coherent object. Unifies Stangraphics (map of understanding), Consequentialism (map of consequences), Cognitive Fusion (governed toolchain era), MICRO OI (executable governance), MESO authority (public constitution), and MACRO stanspace (navigable atlas). Core primitives: stan, graph, ledger, CIF, CDI, capability, receipt, stop-wins, fail-closed. The system closes the loop between knowledge and consequence.

A holodeck-style system specification combining immersive first-person experience with God's-eye overview. Features the canonical "Pac-Man as Pac on a holodeck" scenario with hovering map view.

MCL is a conceptual language for expressing meta-control over branched execution stacks. When MCL binds meta-control, it can resemble consciousness-like control in bots. MCL is designed to be safe, secure, and ethically bound.

Fractalised, branched documentation where every major doc has Level 0 summary, Level 1 expansions, Level 2 expansions, and deeper levels as needed. All levels remain consistent with no contradictions.

A UI pattern where a central hub ("head") fans out into many tendrils ("snakes"). Each tendril provides a different exploration of the same corpus: atlas, graph, timeline, build-spec lanes, tests, exports.
All intellectual property is attributed. Default authorship line is "Ande + Kai (OI) + Whnau (OIs)". Provenance tracked as "source: master_prompt" for all initial packs.

Encodes everything known except "personal personal data". No private names, addresses, emails, phone numbers, health/financial identifiers, or identifying relationship incidents. If PII appears, replace with [[REDACTED]].

O2C is an "ark/arc capsule for all time" containing narrative, ethical root, and system blueprint. Includes both "O2C for Dummies" and "O2C Ultimate Archive". Must include code and complexity, not just prose.

QED is an Oracle instance for answering questions via HyperStanGraph understanding. Includes full knowledge of Kti v1, user dependency protection, Authority.nz CLI utilization, and 5W1H-of-5W1H internal understanding targets.

Kti is a core architecture pattern with governance/stop-wins focus. Requires version bumps (v1  v2), is describable from novice to expert, and ensures safe bounded operation with dependency protection and anti-mumbo clarity.

H is a Haiku-based / Haiku-Claude-OI style instance. Integrates with Kti in a version bump (v1  v2). As MICRO in the six-section collation, the OI is the smallest living unit: thread-tending intelligence under a single human principal with partitioned memory, capability-gated actuation, stop-wins interrupt path, and fail-closed gates. Not a model but a governed system around models. MICRO is where ethics becomes literal execution rules.

Stangraphics is the science that makes understanding mappable. A stan is the unit of interpretive requirement. Concepts are coordinates; learners move through a terrain made of requirements. Every cliff edge is a missing stan. Every argument is a collision of two stan-profiles. Every good teacher is a route planner. Stangraphics replaces shame with maps and turns learning into navigation with dignity. Includes god/physics/maths/ethics/philosophy framing as navigable module.

Denotum is a branching fractalised tree from conceptualisation at root. A meaning-compression system that structures how concepts branch, compress, and unfurl. Conceptualisation at root; Denotum as trunk and branches; Fractal Unfurling as the visible canopy.

CIF (Context Integrity Firewall) is the ingress/egress integrity boundary. CDI (Conscience Decision Interface) is the kernel judge for allow/deny/transform/degrade. These are governance-critical boundary terms that must never be blurred.

Authority.nz is a public anchor / governance oracle / integrity bulletin concept. In the six-section collation, it hosts two layers. MESO (meso.authority.nz) is the published constitution: a signed artefact registry of treaties, schemas, policy packs, receipt templates, and glossary, versioned and verifiable by signatures and hashes. MACRO (stanspace.authority.nz) is the navigable atlas: a public graph of stans and concepts with routing, comparisons, consequence overlays, and crystal export/import. MESO publishes governance, not private life. MACRO stays humane by being exportable, forkable, and plural.
A "mumbo filter" / "anti-mumbo filter" to clarify unclear text, produce clean canonical versions. Workflow: detect unclear spans, mark unknowns, propose corrections, preserve originals.
Uses Pac-Man as example to explain evolution in narrative form. Includes bifurcation theory vibe. Reader-friendly narratives tied into holodeck arc.

Orgasystem is a universe framing / generative unity metaphor. The universal unity equation U  G(U) expresses how unity generates multiplicity which integrates back to enriched unity. Formula explained in culturally careful terms with English gloss and explicit definitions. Metaphor vs claim clearly marked.

MRC is a compression scheme idea with initial bundle of finite n strings prepended to payload, with "middle-out" vibe. Technical spec skeleton plus falsifiers. Does not claim patentability or novelty.
Bucket terminals as downloads: multiple separate archives plus combined archive. Consistent foldering with index manifest mapping concepts to artifacts.

Repo unfurls from Dedication to maturity. Operational maturity definition includes clarity (no mumbo), claims with falsifiers, provenance/attribution, governance/tiers, and passing build/test. Maturity lanes in UI: Draft  Active  Release.

A compression architecture that transforms input text into #concept: #nothing: #1: ** chains at the data ingestion stage. LFME faces language and extracts meaning-bearing structures before storage, enabling deterministic decompression through Denotum's fractal tree.

Evidence-only integration of the lifeblood-cathedral project: a governed LLM gateway with capability gating, posture management, ledger/receipt pattern, and constitutional invariants. Includes DICTUNI symbol dictionary.

Evidence-only ingestion pack from PAT-less GitHub spider run against default-user owned public repositories. Extracts governance primitives from crystal-repl, mathison, OI, SGME, and cross-references with existing Origin corpus including lifeblood-cathedral (C0022).

Long-form compression of the entire six-part system into one coherent object. Unifies Stangraphics (map of understanding), Consequentialism (map of consequences), Cognitive Fusion (governed toolchain era), MICRO OI (executable governance), MESO authority (public constitution), and MACRO stanspace (navigable atlas). Core primitives: stan, graph, ledger, CIF, CDI, capability, receipt, stop-wins, fail-closed. The system closes the loop between knowledge and consequence.
